  "response": "As of October 2023, several smartphones offer great value under \u20b912,000 in India. While the definition of \"best\" can vary based on individual needs and preferences, here are some top contenders that provide excellent performance, features, and user satisfaction in this price range:\n\n1. **Realme Narzo 30**:\n   - **Display**: 6.5-inch Full HD+ LCD\n   - **Processor**: MediaTek Helio G95\n   - **RAM**: 4GB/6GB\n   - **Storage**: 64GB/128GB\n   - **Battery**: 5000mAh with 30W fast charging\n   - **Camera**: Triple rear camera setup (48MP main sensor, 2MP macro, 2MP depth)\n\n2. **Redmi 10 Prime**:\n   - **Display**: 6.5-inch Full HD+ LCD with 90Hz refresh rate\n   - **Processor**: MediaTek Helio G88\n   - **RAM**: 4GB/6GB\n   - **Storage**: 64GB/128GB\n   - **Battery**: 6000mAh with 18W fast charging\n   - **Camera**: Quad camera setup (50MP main sensor, 8MP ultrawide, 2MP macro, 2MP depth)\n\n3. **Samsung Galaxy M12**:\n   - **Display**: 6.5-inch HD+ TFT LCD with 90Hz refresh rate\n   - **Processor**: Exynos 850\n   - **RAM**: 4GB/6GB\n   - **Storage**: 64GB/128GB\n   - **Battery**: 6000mAh with 15W fast charging\n   - **Camera**: Quad camera setup (48MP main sensor, 5MP ultrawide, 2MP macro, 2MP depth)\n\n4. **Poco M3**:\n   - **Display**: 6.53-inch Full HD+ LCD\n   - **Processor**: Qualcomm Snapdragon 662\n   - **RAM**: 4GB/6GB\n   - **Storage**: 64GB/128GB\n   - **Battery**: 6000mAh with 18W fast charging\n   - **Camera**: Triple rear camera setup (48MP main sensor, 2MP macro, 2MP depth)\n\n5. **Micromax IN 2b**:\n   - **Display**: 6.52-inch HD+ LCD\n   - **Processor**: Unisoc T610\n   - **RAM**: 4GB/6GB\n   - **Storage**: 64GB\n   - **Battery**: 5000mAh with 10W charging\n   - **Camera**: Dual camera setup (13MP main sensor, 2MP depth)\n\nChoosing the best smartphone under \u20b912,000 depends on your priorities, such as gaming, camera quality, battery life, or overall performance. It's recommended to check the latest reviews and user feedback to make an informed decision that aligns with your specific needs.",
